Title: Earning at an early age
DateModified: '2019-03-03'
DatePublished: '2019-03-03'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/earning-at-an-early-age
SetInCountry: United Kingdom
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Syed  Ameenuddin
AuthorCountry: India
Text: A boy aged 18 decided to go to study in London for his higher studies and face
  lot of problems while earning and making money to pay his tuition fees. He belongs
  to a very poor family and had Faced a lot of problems while growing up since his
  childhood as his father was uneducated and his father faced lot of problems while
  earning a single penny he used to do lot of hard work to get rid of starving though
  time change and he became a owner of the water bottles company owner and he began
  to start saving the money for his children education expenses his only desire was
  to give his children's the best education as he doesn't want to make his children
  face problems like him.
